appName: I am Chef: Cooking Kitchen VR
displayName: I am Chef: Cooking Kitchen VR
display_name: I am Chef: Cooking Kitchen VR
display_long_description:
I Am Chef: Cooking Kitchen VR, a hands-on kitchen simulator game where you live the true chef life and serve unique animal customers who walk into your restaurant looking for delicious food. Experience a fun yet challenging restaurant simulator where every shift tests your skills as a professional chef.

Take control of real chef job tasks, including food preparation, cooking, grilling, baking, frying, and precise meal plating. Manage continuous food orders, maintain efficient kitchen workflow, and handle intense kitchen chaos as animal clients arrive, wait, and react to your performance. Speed, accuracy, and customer satisfaction are key to success in this fast-paced work simulator.

This immersive cooking simulator features interactive kitchen equipment, realistic cooking mechanics, and skill-based time management gameplay. Serving animal customers adds personality and variety, turning each session into a playful yet demanding kitchen job simulator. From casual cooking moments to high-pressure restaurant rush hours, every action feels physical and rewarding.

I Am Chef: Cooking Kitchen VR blends chef simulator, restaurant management, job simulation, and food game mechanics into one engaging experience. Perfect for players searching for cooking games, chef games, restaurant games, animal restaurant simulators, kitchen games, and realistic simulation games, this title delivers a unique chef roleplay and culinary challenges.
